snippet: Tina Charles scored a career-high 32 points to lead the Liberty to an 87-80 win at home over Maya Moore and the Minnesota Lynx.
abstract: New York Liberty defeat Minnesota Lynx, 87-80 in WNBA action, with Tina Charles scoring a career-high 32 points.
